{"tid":1500490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家入黎睇下先 深層思考停黨鐵一事","createTime":"2019-08-24T04:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T05:26:07.000Z","uid":28843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"31ed25a1d9a94a77d366800e0a6c44f01b1b6971","tid":1500490,"uid":28843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"停咗黨鐵 你地得返馬路有車到觀塘<br />\n出面有啲post講到 人多自然會行出馬路<br />\n咁其實係咪自己友阻住自己友到觀塘呢?<br />\n唔係個個好似啲街坊咁住咁近 有啲真係係大西北黎<br />\n仲有收工既手足呢?<br />\n港共政府如果之後都出呢招 逼黨鐵跪低 其實我地得返馬路 如果馬路都塞車 人聚唔到 咁會唔會本末倒置?<br />\n<br />\n之後所有既不合作運動 我都十分支持 師奶磨袋 跳閘 做一切野令到黨鐵賺小咗<br />\n但係呢一刻 唔係個個香港人有車 而家仲要有車都未必去到 所有物資 人員都去唔到現場<br />\n<br />\n所以 三思 堵路既可行性 你塞一塞條觀塘道 基本上一定倒灌 所以我唔建議堵觀塘道 其他我冇意見<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"2e6d17351251e7a5e22a60b692f3ca4a6985e6cf","tid":1500490,"uid":28843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"721 十連推"},{"pid":"b30d256bf9db4e346ced24fec8a693c3ff165f76","tid":1500490,"uid":28843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:45:37.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"c6d88999d47e6b48ff64c183cf2978ecccdfb304","tid":1500490,"uid":28843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:47:18.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"536fe4e2185287f660dd0892c02c8de86b0e38b4","tid":1500490,"uid":28843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:47:38.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"c7989fea23fa37eeda42a8c16f9054f4bff45315","tid":1500490,"uid":28843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:48:30.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"adbe28bc0a448c1ec03ccb2cd205c0e2f1fc6909","tid":1500490,"uid":28843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:48:58.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"d64ef7026d1a84a6740fa020843a914ec2d60fc6","tid":1500490,"uid":28843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:49:21.000Z","msg":"721"},